237
00:10:46,738 --> 00:10:48,940
<i>- It turned out nicely.</i>
<i>- It's really pretty.</i>

238
00:10:49,040 --> 00:10:50,609
<i>- Thank you.</i>
<i>- It has a touch of flair, too.</i>

239
00:10:50,675 --> 00:10:52,911
